1. *Brzinu* njegovog trčanja je bilo teško zaustaviti. (It was hard to stop the speed of his running.)
2. Oni su zaustavili *brzinu* automobila na ograničenoj saobraćajnoj zoni. (They stopped the speed of the car in a restricted traffic zone.)
3. Ovi automobili imaju da poboljšaju *brzinu* njihovog pokretanja. (These cars have to improve the speed of their startup.)
4. *Brzinu* svetlosti je nemoguće prekoračiti. (It is impossible to exceed the speed of light.)
5. Ljudi su se začudili *brzini* njegovog pisanja. (People were amazed at the speed of his writing.)